title: Kono Healer, Mendokusai (This Healer's a Handful)
synopsis: A fantasy and adventure comedy starring Karla, a dark elf cleric who invested too much in her insulting skills, and Alvin, a swordsman who has to put up with her antics.
staff: [['Nakanishi, Nobuaki', ['Director']], ['Shimo, Fumihiko', ['Script', ' Series Composition']], ['Tannen ni Hakkou', ['Original Creator']], ['Kikunaga, Chisato', ['Character Design']]]
